{"id":150203,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/亚琛和平奖获奖者名单公布/","date":"2011-05-06T14:30:27Z","modified":"2011-05-06T14:30:27Z","title":"亚琛和平奖获奖者名单公布","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚琛</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">2011年度亚琛和平奖的获奖人是反军备人士和组织。亚琛和平奖联合会周五（5月6日）宣布，弗莱堡市民于尔根·格雷斯林（</span><span>J</span><span>ü</span><span>rgen Gr</span><span>ä</span><span>sslin</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和图宾根的军事化信息中心被授予本年度亚琛和平奖。该奖旨在表彰“从底层”致力于和平事业的卓越人士和组织，颁奖典礼于每年的</span><span>9<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span>1<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日—“反战日”举行。今年的奖金额为</span>2000<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧元。亚琛和评奖联合会在解释今年的授奖决定时指出，格雷斯林从</span>1980<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年代起就不知疲倦地、并以给人印象深刻的精力投入和平事业；信息中心则以其对全球军事化趋势的分析成了科学与和平运动之间的“铰链”。亚琛和平奖于</span>1988<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年设立，该奖联合会现有大约</span>350<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名个人成员和</span>50<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个组织。</span></span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15056295%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%BA%9A%E7%90%9B%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%A5%96%E8%8E%B7%E5%A5%96%E8%80%85%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=